Curcumae rhizoma and its major constituents against hepatobiliary disease: 
Pharmacotherapeutic properties and potential clinical applications.

Gao TH(1), Liao W(2), Lin LT(3), Zhu ZP(3), Lu MG(4), Fu CM(3), Xie T(5).

Author information:
(1)State Key Laboratory of Southwestern Chinese Medicine Resources, Pharmacy 
College, Chengdu University of Traditional Chinese Medicine, Chengdu 611137, 
