Ginger for Healthy Ageing: A Systematic Review on Current Evidence of Its 
Antioxidant, Anti-Inflammatory, and Anticancer Properties.

Ozkur M(1), Benlier N(1), Takan I(2)(3), Vasileiou C(4), Georgakilas AG(4), 
Pavlopoulou A(2)(3), Cetin Z(5)(6), Saygili EI(7)(8).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medical Pharmacology, Faculty of Medicine, SANKO University, 
Gaziantep, Turkey.
(2)Izmir Biomedicine and Genome Center, Balcova, Izmir 35340, Turkey.
(3)Izmir International Biomedicine and Genome Institute, Dokuz Eylül University, 
Balcova, Izmir 35220, Turkey.
(4)DNA Damage Laboratory, Physics Department, School of Applied Mathematical and 
Physical Sciences, National Technical University of Athens, 157 80 Athens, 
